name: Wardens of the Tonal Tides
description: Hailing from the Rootmason capital city of Thespin, the Wardens of the Tonal Tides are known far and wide for their affinity with all manner of woodwind. Now experienced navigators that captain liquefaction-based transport systems, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
